lead_paragraph: Deshaun Watson will always remember the day he walked into a home he could call his own. It was just before Thanksgiving in 2006, a rather brisk day in the suburbs north of Atlanta.

headline.print_headline: Keys to a Home Gave Deshaun Watson and Family a New Start
